---
import { ImageReveal, ScrollWithFade } from 'skiper-islands'
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6 bg-brand-surface">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
    <ImageReveal direction="left">
      <img
        src="https://picsum.photos/seed/watchmaker+workshop+natural+light/700/800"
        alt="Watchmaker workshop"
        class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </ImageReveal>
    <ScrollWithFade>
      <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-label text-brand-text-secondary mb-4">Our story</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-[2.5rem] text-brand-primary mb-6 leading-[1.15]">Every watch starts with a question.</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-brand-primary mb-4">
        Most watch brands start with a movement. We start with a moment: the feeling of
        watching the sun set over the Java Sea and wondering what time it is back home.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-brand-text-secondary mb-9">
        Sela is designed for people who live across time zones not because they have to,
        but because the people they love live somewhere else. Every watch we make is a
        translation of that feeling into something you can wear on your wrist.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/about" class="inline-block bg-brand-accent text-white px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-brand-accent-hover transition-colors duration-300">
          Meet the designer
        </a>
        <a href="/design-process" class="inline-block border border-brand-primary text-brand-primary px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-brand-primary hover:text-brand-background transition-colors duration-300">
          See our process
        </a>
      </div>
    </ScrollWithFade>
  </div>
</section>
